VBA method for Excel:
```vb
Sub DeleteRows()
    Dim r As Long
    For r = Cells(Rows.Count, "I").End(xlUp).Row To 2 Step -1
        If Cells(r, "I").Value <> "" And Cells(r, "H").Value = "" Then
            Rows(r).Delete
        End If
    Next r
End Sub
```

